OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782011884
OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FAt least seven people including two
OL,7,Fchildren have been killed in Israeli
OL,8,Fairstrikes on Lebanon less than one
OL,9,Fday after a ceasefire agreement was
OL,10,Freported in the region.
OL,12,FStrikes hit the southern town of
OL,13,FNabatiyeh and nearby villages on
OL,14,FSaturday, and at least seven people
OL,15,Fwere trapped under the rubble,
OL,16,FLebanon's National News Agency said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
