OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FAn Israeli military official said
OL,7,FHezbollah had fired more than 50
OL,8,Fprojectiles at Israeli forces in
OL,9,Fsouthern Lebanon overnight, prompting
OL,10,Fforces to start targeting the militant
OL,11,Fgroup there.
