OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FOn Friday, Israel and Hezbollah were
OL,7,Fsaid to have agreed to an immediate
OL,8,Fceasefire by US officials, after the
OL,9,Fongoing strikes impacted talks between
OL,10,FWashington and Tehran.
OL,12,FThe ceasefire was said to begin at 4pm
OL,13,Flocal time, or 2pm BST following a
OL,14,Fheavy exchange that killed at least 47
OL,15,Fpeople in Lebanon and four Israeli
OL,16,Fsoldiers on Friday.
OL,18,FJD Vance had been due to begin talks
OL,19,Fin Switzerland this week, but Iranian
OL,20,Fofficials said they would not meet
OL,21,Funless the fighting had stopped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
