PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782011884
OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FFollowing the reports of a truce,
OL,7,FIsraeli ambassador to Washington,
OL,8,FYechiel Leiter, said on X that Israel
OL,9,F"remains firmly committed to an
OL,10,Fimmediate ceasefire" if Hezbollah also
OL,11,Fhonours the agreement.
OL,13,FHezbollah has said in public
OL,14,Fstatements it will abide by a
OL,15,Fceasefire if Israel does, but has not
OL,16,Fsaid a ceasefire was actually in place.
OL,18,FThe Israeli strikes on the village of
OL,19,FBarish killed four members of a
OL,20,Ffamily, two parents and two children,
OL,21,FLebanon's National News Agency said.
