OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FIn Arab Salim village, a body was
OL,7,Fpulled from a destroyed house, and in
OL,8,Fthe villages of Doueir and Kfar
OL,9,FRumman, drone strikes killed a person
OL,10,Fon a motorcycle and a Lebanese soldier.
OL,12,FMilitary spokesman Brigadier General
OL,13,FEffie Defrin said the Israeli forces
OL,14,Fwere operating in a "forward defense
OL,15,Fzone" and would continue doing so.
OL,26,@vD@UOUwD@EO]
