OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FIsrael's Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,7,FNetanyahu has not commented on the
OL,8,Fceasefire efforts, but said the
OL,9,FIsraeli army had "struck powerfully"
OL,10,F150 Hezbollah targets, killing dozens
OL,11,Fof militants on Friday.
OL,13,FThe nation's minister for national
OL,14,Fsecurity, Itamar Ben-Gvir, said "all
OL,15,Fof Lebanon must burn" and the nation
OL,16,Fneeded to "go beserk" in a tirade
OL,17,Fposted on X the same day.
OL,19,F"For every tear of an Israeli mother,
OL,20,Fa thousand Lebanese mothers must
OL,21,Fweep," Ben-Gvir said.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
