OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FThe Iran-US calls for the "immediate
OL,7,Fand permanent" end of military
OL,8,Foperations on "all fronts", including
OL,9,FLebanon.
OL,11,FThe interim deal gives negotiators 60
OL,12,Fdays to make their agreement, but this
OL,13,Fcan be extended.
OL,15,FIran's Foreign Ministry spokesman
OL,16,FEsmail Baghaei said negotiation
OL,17,Fefforts would continue on Saturday,
OL,18,Fwith Pakistan's interior minister due
OL,19,Fto arrive for talks, according to the
OL,20,Fnation's semi-official ISNA news
OL,21,Fagency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
