PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782011884
OL,3,CIsraeli airstrikes kill at least seven
OL,4,Cin Lebanon hours after ceasefire
OL,6,FBaghaei had said consultations through
OL,7,Fmediators were ongoing regarding the
OL,8,Fnext phase of negotiations to draft a
OL,9,Ffinal US-Iran agreement.
OL,11,FBecause the initial deal was signed
OL,12,Fdigitally earlier this week, the talks
OL,13,Fin Switzerland were not urgent, and
OL,14,Fplans were underway to hold a meeting
OL,15,Fin the coming days, he said.
